I'll give an account of you, and your Proceedings. If Indiscretion be a sign of Love, you are the most a Lover of any Body that I know: You fancy that parting with your Estate, will help you to your Mistress.—In my mind he is a thoughtless Adventurer,


VVho hopes to purchase VVealth, by selling Land;

Or win a Mistress, with a losing hand.
